--- install module ---
	1. make
	2. copy pam_shamir.so in /lib/security (depend of your system (lib32/lib64/x86_64-linux-gnu/...)
	3. chown root:root pam_shamir.so
	4. chmod 644 pam_shamir.so

--- configure pam ---
	1. edit /etc/pam.d/login and add this line to the top of the file (adapt the module path):
		auth	optional	/lib/security/pam_shamir.so
	
--- testing module ---
	1. open a tty and try to connect
	2. get the last lines in your /var/auth.log
	3. If you see a line like that, you win ! 
		pam_shamir.so[1065]: Test message from pam_shamir
	4. else, contact the developper

